               stealing, on the <rs id="t18261207-160-cd945" type="crimeDate">8th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18261207-160-off944 t18261207-160-cd945"></join>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18261207-160-off946 t18261207-160-cd945"></join>, 1 purse, value 18d.; 8 sovereigns, and a 5l. note, the property of 
